snippet.title: Treasure Cove for the Bally Astrocade
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

In Treasure Cove , the player takes the role of a diver, who has to collect gold coins, which are on the bottom of an ocean.

The diver will run out of oxygen if he is too long underwater, and has to sswim back to the boat in time.

There are also various sea animals, which the diver has to avoid. 
In evevery level comes a new sea animal.


What I think:

Okay gameplay, with awesome music and well-made sprites.
